Bryan Roberts wins the Seventh Annual Clifton Memorial Book Prize
%%%
<p>
The Seventh Annual Clifton Memorial Book Prize has been awarded to Bryan Roberts
of the University of Pittsburgh for his "Time Reversal and the Symmetry of Nothing."
</p>
